ential for severe interaction.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/23235/', '', 'Lincomycin, Dirithromycin', 'Indapamide, Bempedoic acid, Perindopril, Fenofibric acid, Pitavastatin, Evinacumab, Evolocumab, Dextrothyroxine, Cholestyramine, Clofibrate, Colestipol, More', 1767369485);
