, Valsartan, Rosuvastatin, Lisinopril, Perindopril, Niacin, Pravastatin, Acetylsalicylic acid, Ezetimibe, Bempedoic acid, Indapamide, More', 'Lincomycin, Dirithromycin', 1767369485);
